Build tools

<p>
<a href="http://mamedev.org/tools/">MSYS2</a> based tools are now available for download.<br/>
<br/>
Tools updated to version 2016-02-16, if you have some of previous versions please update.<br/>
<br>
Since way of handling MAME depending updates is now done using pacman package manager we recommend<br/>
you to install clean copy of tools.
</p>
